    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "data": {},
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Core variables",
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "data": {},
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Core variables relate to a specific context or abstraction. Core variable helps communicate the intended purpose of a variable, and are effective when a value with a single intent will appear in multiple places."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "data": {},
    "children": [
      {
