    "data": {},
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Color classes",
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "data": {},
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Color classes are sets of semantic and additional colors grouped in classes to use in colored components."
